'''迪吉彭理工學院'''（{{lang-en|'''DigiPen Institute of Technology'''}}）是位於[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]][[雷德蒙德_(華盛頓州)|雷德蒙德]]的一家[[營利學校|營利性]] <ref>{{cite web|title=DigiPen Institute of Technology|url=https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/college-university-search/digi-pen-institute-of-technology|publisher=College Board|accessdate=14 November 2012|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192045/https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/college-university-search/digi-pen-institute-of-technology|dead-url=yes}}</ref>私立高等教育机构，在[[新加坡|新加坡]]、西班牙[[畢爾巴鄂|畢爾巴鄂]]有分校區，學員提供本科及研究生課程。

迪吉彭理工學院由{{Link-en|美国职业学校和学院认证委员会|Accrediting Commission of Career Schools and Colleges}}认证<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://www.digipen.edu/about/accreditation/ |title= DigiPen: Accreditation |publisher= DigiPen Institute of Technology |language= en |5=  |accessdate= 2014-05-20 |archive-date= 2014-03-28 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140328180724/https://www.digipen.edu/about/accreditation/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

該學院的前身是{{Link-en|克勞德·科馬爾|Claude Comair}}在1988年創建於加拿大[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]的一家電腦動畫公司。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digipen.edu/academics/course-catalog/rules-and-policies/general-information/ |title=DigiPen: General Information |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201006/https://www.digipen.edu/academics/course-catalog/rules-and-policies/general-information/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 1998年1月搬至雷德蒙德[[任天堂软件技术|任天堂软件技术]]大楼内。2010年8月搬入在北雷德蒙德擴建的新主校區，此校區面積為{{convert|9300|m2}}。<ref>[http://www.pnwlocalnews.com/east_king/red/news/101833653.html DigiPen celebrates new, bigger location on Willows Road] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100903125421/http://www.pnwlocalnews.com/east_king/red/news/101833653.html |date=2010-09-03 }}</ref>

== 排名==
* 根據[[世界大學網路排名|世界大學網路排名]]，該大學於2011年1月處於大約兩萬所大學中的第五千九百名。<ref>[http://www.webometrics.info/top12000.asp?offset=5900&zoom_highlight=digipen ''Webometrics Ranking Web of World Universities''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319193229/http://www.webometrics.info/top12000.asp?offset=5900&zoom_highlight=digipen |date=2012-03-19 }}</ref>
*2010年，[[普林斯頓評論|普林斯頓評論]]將其評為遊戲設計界第二學府。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110607071932/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/214164/8-highest-ranked-colleges-for-game-design/ 8 Highest-Ranked Colleges for Game Design, Feature Story from GamePro]</ref>

